column5: so I went to the website to see if ice was forming on simcoe and saw this      but then I figured it out, it was clouds not ice oh well it will come when it comes here is the link to the sat. pictures  sat pictures  click here
Dang! Looks like size 12 prints to me!
No ice fishing yet, I need one more perch outing after getting skunked in BOQ
Unless your Jesus, you'd be best to wait for Simcoe!
Next Saturday, Paul?  Feelin' a little jiggy myself.
if I remember my JUDEO CHRISTIAN  upbringing Moses parted the water JC walked on it was a fisherman too

Well Terry I hope you find the guy who can freeze it quickly because my 9 year old son has informed me that he wants to return with uncle Dan(Percher)for some non stop fat perch action.Hopefully we will be back soon.Mike
I hear ya Paul!!! If ya can't tangle with the big one, whip up on the little ones!   I plan to open a can of Whoop-ass on the Crappie here for the next few months!
